&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl">hans -&amp;gt; defendants: &amp;#39;起诉要求1亿美元&amp;#39;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl"># 冒犯
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl">defendants.naka -&amp;gt; hans: 在直播中指控作弊
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">21&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl">defendants.mc -&amp;gt; hans: 败失后退出并指控
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">22&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl">defendants.chesscom -&amp;gt; hans: 72页作弊报告
