&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl"> John--&amp;gt;Alice: Great!
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl"> John-&amp;gt;Bob: How about you?
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl"> Bob--&amp;gt;John: Jolly good!
